channel.title: RSPS Banners
channel.description:
Hey! I just downloaded Photoshop CS6, and i want to learn all the diffrent tools in it, so might as well help people while learning right? Yes yes, i stole this idea from runelocos, who cares? I'll make RSPS banners for you if you want.:) *WARNING* They will probably not be that great. Just post this infromation.
Primary Text(Server Name): Secondary Text(Probably a quote, for example "Your search ends here"): Primary Color: Secondary color: Background or transparent?: Image for background? (Only if selected background): Anything else? (eg. Extra images such as Dragon claws): IMPORTANT: Would you like a medium or big banner, if so please give exact pixel size:
Examples: [URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/801/78545574.jpg/][IMG]http://img801.imageshack.us/img801/6654/78545574.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/36/backgroundvr.jpg/][IMG]http://img36.imageshack.us/img36/7519/backgroundvr.jpg[/img][/URL]
